<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html lang="en-US">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"  />
    <title>美人相机积分</title>
    <link href="css/beauty-point.css" type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/fastclick.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        window.addEventListener( "load", function() {
            FastClick.attach( document.body );
        }, false );
    </script>
    <body class="bg-fff">
        <section class="experience-page">
            <div class="banner-item">
                <img src="images/test/750x450.jpg" />
            </div>
            <div class="con-wrap">
                <div class="listItem">体验云相册</div>
                <div class="item-list">
                    <div class="item">
                        <h3 class="title">
                            <span class="area">任务详情</span>
                        </h3>
                        <div class="text-item">
                            <p>进入云相册，上传一张照片即可获得奖励积分。如果采用“在线支付”方式完成订单，首次上传10张照片即可获取200积分奖励。</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="item">
                        <h3 class="title">
                            <span class="area">奖励积分</span>
                            <span class="tips-item">
                                <i class="icon points-icon"></i>
                                <span class="points-item">+<em class="num">3</em></span>
                            </span>
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="mod-btn-item">
                    <a href="#" class="now-btn" style="display:none">立即体验</a>
                    <a href="#" class="now-btn finish-btn">已安装</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </body>
</html>